{"id": 1703, "genre": 1001, "title": "你会因为怕尴尬而放弃购买哪些东西？", "description": "自己花钱，有时候也不能随心所欲。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 3443, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170525141230g931fRBeNrYCpt6E.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-27T03:00:07Z", "options": [{"id": 207872, "content": "情趣內衣", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026528}, {"id": 207873, "content": "评论说的我都敢买，要不我做个代购吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1041752}, {"id": 207874, "content": "衣服  鞋子实体店，社恐患者进这类店都尴尬，放弃购买哈哈哈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 799183}, {"id": 208132, "content": "印度神油", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 928584}, {"id": 207878, "content": "和朋友一起逛街，有时候商场花车里的东西会不好意思去看，更别提买了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 208647, "content": "现在开始思考这个设问", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 109936}, {"id": 207880, "content": "杂志摊里的色情杂志", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935385}, {"id": 207885, "content": "摆在商厂门口的打折文胸和内裤", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1041869}, {"id": 207888, "content": "同款不同色的衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 518227}, {"id": 207889, "content": "时时刻刻'z", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977444}, {"id": 207890, "content": "内裤", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1018761}, {"id": 208402, "content": "衣服这些吧 太贵买不起", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1043271}, {"id": 207891, "content": "旺仔牛奶", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036853}, {"id": 208403, "content": "避孕套，脱毛膏这辈子都不会在超市买的东东", "image": "img/option/option/20170530010023XrAlYKw1kb36E8eG", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1043276}, {"id": 208660, "content": "衣服鞋子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1027566}, {"id": 208916, "content": "星巴克算吗……“我要一杯摩卡可可碎片星冰乐大杯”名字太长了！！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 980278}, {"id": 207893, "content": "给女友买内衣", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1041932}, {"id": 207895, "content": "我不会把能穿的旧衣服丢了所以也不买新衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1014210}, {"id": 207896, "content": "北京方便面", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235507}, {"id": 207903, "content": "没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 882260}, {"id": 207904, "content": "在不是学校的地方买辣条，买的时候感觉尬尬的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678053}, {"id": 207905, "content": "你们不敢买的 都交给我   价格便宜保真 找代购就找我", "image": "img/option/option/201705281041013pexRDVNWXYH2uOL.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1042038}, {"id": 207906, "content": "啤酒?甚至果啤  我是女生 人家都会用异样眼光看着我❗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038144}, {"id": 207907, "content": "书店前面的促销书本  还有冬天里买雪糕", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038144}, {"id": 211235, "content": "不去屈臣氏，我还是个孩纸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050961}, {"id": 207908, "content": "最尴尬的事情是没钱 其余都没啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 504539}, {"id": 207909, "content": "店员太热情的店，不敢去", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039390}, {"id": 210213, "content": "任何店员帅气有型或者太过好看的店\n都不太敢去买东西(比如我生活在米兰 奢侈品街上每一家店的店员都像是模特)", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1049284}, {"id": 207910, "content": "和同学一起逛街不敢乱买怕被背后嚼舌根??‍♀️", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1042077}, {"id": 208422, "content": "情趣用品", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1017071}, {"id": 207911, "content": "等身抱枕...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973320}, {"id": 211495, "content": "避孕药", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1051651}, {"id": 207912, "content": "避孕套\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 514176}, {"id": 208168, "content": "游戏点卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1042844}, {"id": 210731, "content": "烤串臭豆腐麻辣烫", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 872374}, {"id": 210220, "content": "尴尬就是  被问你能买得起吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1048874}, {"id": 207917, "content": "手机……没钱啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957754}, {"id": 207918, "content": "跟服务的小哥小姐姐多两眼对视就。尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770560}, {"id": 212014, "content": "化妆品，因为自己并不是很会化妆，但又想看看", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016527}, {"id": 207919, "content": "衛生用品", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921750}, {"id": 208175, "content": "并没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1042162}, {"id": 207920, "content": "服务员一直跟着，还问我要买什么，我特么就是逛一逛，算了，不逛了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 653221}, {"id": 207921, "content": "不脱单不再买内衣套装…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759580}, {"id": 208945, "content": "内衣 ?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1018477}, {"id": 207923, "content": "鞋的款式很喜欢，但大街上几乎人人都穿这种款式", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 95254}, {"id": 209203, "content": "超市里的化妆品区，不夸张，一条道至少站着四位导购员。走进去感觉就要被围攻……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1046001}, {"id": 211252, "content": "太贵的耳机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001162}, {"id": 207926, "content": "大姨妈", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1042222}, {"id": 210231, "content": "你懂的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937678}, {"id": 207928, "content": "我根本就没有买！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1012175}]}